      "FunctionSignature": "DynRenga.Converters.Renga.MeshConverter.ExportedObjectToBoundingBox@DynRenga.RengaAPI.IExportedObject3D",
      "Replication": "Auto",
      "Description": "Compute the overall bounding box for an exported object using the same finite-vertex filtering logic as ExportedObjectToDynamoGeometry. Returns null if no finite vertices found.\n\nMeshConverter.ExportedObjectToBoundingBox (exported: IExportedObject3D): BoundingBox"
    },
    {
